quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,179,"Soni chisimu chene twajiguumbiile Jahannama majini gamajinji kwisa soni ŵandu (ŵatakajinjileko), ŵanganyao akwete mitima nambo ŵangamanyilila najo, meso soni akwete nambo ŵangalolela nago, ni mawiwi gakwe akwete nambo ŵangapikanila nago, ŵanganyao ali chisawu inyama, gambakuti ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵakusokonechela nnope (kumpunda inyama), ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵaakwaanjila (malamusi ga Allah)"
  7,180,"Soni Allah jukwete mena gambone nnope, basi mum’bombani nago, ni mwaleche aŵala ŵaakugapombotasya mena Gakwe, chachilipidwa pa yaŵaliji nkupanganya"
  7,181,"Soni mu ŵandu ŵatwagumbile, mwana likuga lyalikwaajongolela (achimijao) ku yakuona, soni ni yakuonayo akutendaga chilungamiko"
  7,182,"Soni aŵala ŵaakaaniile ma Ȃya Getu, chitwajigale mbolembole wa ku ipotesi kupitila m’matala gangaakugamanyilila"
  7,183,"Soni ngamba kwalechelela ŵanganyao, chisimu mpango Wangu uŵele wakulimbangana"
  7,184,"Ana ngaakuchetelela? Mwa n'jaomotu mwangali masoka, nganaŵa jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) ikaŵeje nkutetela jwakuonechela"
  7,185,"Ana ngaakuuona uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, ni ichindu yosope yaagumbile Allah, soni yanti mwine komboleka kuŵa ndaŵi jao jakuwila jiŵandichile? Ana ni abalichi panyuma paaji (Quraniji) jatachijikulupilila"
  7,186,"Mundu jwannechelele Allah kusokonechela, basi nganakola nkun'jongola, ni akwalekaga nkusokonechela mwaomo achiyumbagayumbaga"
  7,187,"Akum'buusya (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ya ndema (jakwichila Kiyama kuti): “Jichiŵa chakachi?” Jilani: “Chisimu umanyilisi wakwe uli kwa Ambuje ŵangu pe. Pangali ŵampaka ajionesye papaswela ndaŵi jakwe ikaŵeje Jwalakwe. Jisitwepe kumawunde ni petaka. Ngasijim'bichilila ikaŵeje mwachisupuchisya.” Akum'buusya nti chisawu mmwejo m'bele ŵakuwuchilichisya ya jalakwejo (ni mpaka n'jimaanyi ndaŵi jakwe). Jilani: “Chisimu umanyilisi wakwe uli kwa Allah, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ngaakumanyilila.”"